1
00:00:43,060 --> 00:00:46,780
=Auspicious Nobles=

2
00:00:47,580 --> 00:00:49,940
=Episode 19=

3
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:52,500
(This Crown Prince Makes People
Want to Break the Law)

4
00:00:58,100 --> 00:01:00,740
(Banknote)

5
00:01:07,350 --> 00:01:08,790
Tower Master, the bank...

6
00:01:08,790 --> 00:01:10,000
The bank is on fire!

7
00:01:12,950 --> 00:01:14,150
Burning again?

8
00:01:15,070 --> 00:01:16,480
Zheng Yuanhe!

9
00:01:16,480 --> 00:01:18,050
You won't stop until I'm dead, will you?

10
00:01:18,510 --> 00:01:19,350
I knew it.

11
00:01:19,430 --> 00:01:21,120
That lunatic never believed me.

12
00:01:21,700 --> 00:01:24,000
Tower Master, the Crown Prince
has broken in with his men!

13
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:25,580
Commander Jiu
is holding them off at the front.

14
00:01:25,590 --> 00:01:27,070
We're here to escort you out.

15
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:36,200
The bank was just set on fire.
Now they've come straight here.

16
00:01:36,210 --> 00:01:38,350
They're really determined
to wipe us out, aren't they?

17
00:01:38,360 --> 00:01:39,840
Tower Master, as long as there's hope...

18
00:01:39,840 --> 00:01:40,640
I'll stay.

19
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:43,760
Pack up everything important.

20
00:01:43,870 --> 00:01:44,480
Let's go!

21
00:02:29,750 --> 00:02:30,710
Li

22
00:02:32,030 --> 00:02:33,080
Qing

23
00:02:34,630 --> 00:02:35,750
qing?

24
00:04:03,470 --> 00:04:04,470
We're doomed.

25
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:07,870
I came to Great Yong
to make something of myself,

26
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:11,000
and now I've become an accessory.

27
00:04:12,150 --> 00:04:13,150
Zheng Yuanhe.

28
00:04:13,910 --> 00:04:15,520
You may be insufferable,

29
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:17,560
but please don't die here.

30
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:20,070
Please...

31
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:34,870
He's...

32
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:36,560
He's still alive.

33
00:04:36,560 --> 00:04:37,310
Let's go.

34
00:04:37,400 --> 00:04:38,870
The Inspectorate is searching this way.

35
00:04:38,870 --> 00:04:40,190
Come on. Bring him with us.

36
00:04:40,870 --> 00:04:42,290
If you want to get rid of the body,

37
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,720
just dump him in some cave.

38
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,120
What body?

39
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:47,160
He's still alive.

40
00:04:47,310 --> 00:04:48,390
Come on, give me a hand.

41
00:04:48,750 --> 00:04:49,630
Your Highness!

42
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:50,560
Your Highness!

43
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:51,920
- Your Highness!
- Your Highness!

44
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:53,560
- Your Highness!
- Your Highness!

45
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:54,160
Your Highness!

46
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:55,870
- Your Highness!
- Your Highness!

47
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,070
General Chang Lin!

48
00:04:57,160 --> 00:04:59,240
- Where are you, Your Highness?
- Your Highness!

49
00:04:59,240 --> 00:04:59,800
General Chang Lin!

50
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:00,390
Your Highness!

51
00:05:00,390 --> 00:05:01,670
We've searched the entire ravine.

52
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:03,240
There's no sign of His Highness.

53
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:04,360
That's impossible.

54
00:05:05,190 --> 00:05:06,920
I saw His Highness
fall with my own eyes.

55
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:08,040
Could it be

56
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:10,040
that His Highness
was taken by those rebels?

57
00:05:10,270 --> 00:05:11,830
Or perhaps they threw him into...

58
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,270
I spoke out of turn.

59
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:15,870
Until His Highness is found,

60
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:18,750
no one is to breathe a word of this.

61
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:19,680
- Yes.
- Yes.

62
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:26,480
They'll never expect us to come back.

63
00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:28,510
That's exactly
why this is the safest place.

64
00:05:29,070 --> 00:05:30,610
Zheng Yuanhe cannot be allowed to live.

65
00:05:32,390 --> 00:05:33,630
If you kill him,

66
00:05:33,750 --> 00:05:35,070
everyone at Wangshi Tower

67
00:05:35,070 --> 00:05:36,670
will spend the rest
of their lives on the run.

68
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:38,120
Even if we don't kill him,

69
00:05:38,800 --> 00:05:39,950
the outcome will be the same.

70
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:41,690
Once he wakes up,
do you really think he'll let us go?

71
00:05:41,830 --> 00:05:44,040
As long as he's alive,
there's still hope.

72
00:05:44,400 --> 00:05:45,560
We'll keep him alive for now.

73
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:47,750
All he wants is the throne.

74
00:05:48,160 --> 00:05:49,070
When he wakes up,

75
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:49,950
I'll talk to him.

76
00:05:50,630 --> 00:05:51,680
And if he won't negotiate?

77
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:54,680
Then...

78
00:05:55,510 --> 00:05:57,830
don't blame me.

79
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:01,600
Your Majesty,

80
00:06:01,870 --> 00:06:04,310
the Crown Prince remains missing.

81
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:06,750
The Inspectorate
cannot remain leaderless.

82
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:07,830
I humbly ask Your Majesty

83
00:06:07,830 --> 00:06:10,430
to appoint someone to oversee
its affairs as soon as possible.

84
00:06:12,270 --> 00:06:13,480
I second the motion.

85
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:16,750
Furthermore,
while confined to his residence,

86
00:06:16,760 --> 00:06:18,030
the Crown Prince
left without authorization.

87
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:19,190
His reckless conduct

88
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:21,750
put himself in grave danger.

89
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:24,950
He is unfit to bear the responsibility
of being Crown Prince.

90
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:27,120
I earnestly ask Your Majesty,

91
00:06:27,430 --> 00:06:29,040
for the sake of the empire,

92
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,560
to appoint a wiser successor.

93
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:34,040
Your Majesty,
for the sake of the empire,

94
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:36,040
please appoint a wiser successor.

95
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:39,430
Zhao,

96
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,920
do you think so as well?

97
00:06:43,950 --> 00:06:44,830
Father,

98
00:06:45,310 --> 00:06:46,480
I believe

99
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:49,160
our top priority
should be finding Yuanhe.

100
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:52,600
I agree.

101
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:54,480
The affairs of the Inspectorate

102
00:06:54,500 --> 00:06:56,690
will be placed under
the Second Prince's supervision for now.

103
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:57,950
As for everything else,

104
00:06:58,430 --> 00:07:01,040
we'll discuss it
after the Crown Prince is found.

105
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:08,480
- We bid Your Majesty farewell.
- We bid Your Majesty farewell.

106
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:10,360
(Just as I thought.)

107
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:13,160
(No matter how Father acts,)

108
00:07:13,510 --> 00:07:15,430
(the one he cares about most)

109
00:07:15,430 --> 00:07:17,070
(is still Zheng Yuanhe.)

110
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:21,920
Tower Master,

111
00:07:22,270 --> 00:07:24,070
it's a real shame
the bank was destroyed.

112
00:07:24,430 --> 00:07:26,270
May I ask what your plans are now?

113
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:28,040
Forget it.

114
00:07:28,270 --> 00:07:30,070
The Crown Prince is dead anyway.

115
00:07:30,510 --> 00:07:31,510
I'm tired too.

116
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:33,510
This is a good chance to take a break.

117
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:36,240
As for making money,

118
00:07:36,510 --> 00:07:37,800
that can wait.

119
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:42,000
Tower Master, have a good rest.

120
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,040
I'll come visit you another day.

121
00:07:58,800 --> 00:07:59,800
Tower Master,

122
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:01,310
are we really not making money anymore?

123
00:08:01,390 --> 00:08:02,160
Then little goal...

124
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:02,750
We are.

125
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:04,270
Of course we are.

126
00:08:04,280 --> 00:08:06,070
Just not with Yuanzhao
for the time being.

127
00:08:07,270 --> 00:08:08,040
Why not?

128
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:10,830
Looking back at how
the workshop was exposed,

129
00:08:10,830 --> 00:08:12,360
that arrow that day...

130
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:13,430
Other than me,

131
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:17,430
the one who stood to gain the most
from Zheng Yuanhe's death was Yuanzhao.

132
00:08:18,070 --> 00:08:19,800
Every time he came blindfolded,

133
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:21,920
he still knew
the workshop's exact location.

134
00:08:22,230 --> 00:08:24,000
That means he'd been
pretending to play dumb

135
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:25,240
right in front of me all along.

136
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:31,160
And that's the frightening part.

137
00:08:32,940 --> 00:08:35,380
(Wangshi Tower)

138
00:08:58,030 --> 00:08:58,840
Who are you?

139
00:09:00,550 --> 00:09:01,670
You don't remember me?

140
00:09:11,030 --> 00:09:12,550
Then do you remember

141
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:14,270
who you are?

142
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:17,440
I...

143
00:09:20,150 --> 00:09:21,080
Who am I?

144
00:09:29,030 --> 00:09:31,270
(Looks like he's not faking it.)

145
00:09:32,270 --> 00:09:35,030
(What a perfect chance for revenge.)

146
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:37,840
You are

147
00:09:38,270 --> 00:09:39,550
my servant.

148
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:48,270
No way.

149
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:54,510
From now on,

150
00:09:54,510 --> 00:09:56,390
call me Master before you speak.

151
00:09:57,840 --> 00:10:00,360
I said you're my servant, so you are.

152
00:10:02,700 --> 00:10:04,660
Who gave you permission
to glare at your master like that?

153
00:10:04,670 --> 00:10:05,370
You deserve that.

154
00:10:07,750 --> 00:10:09,270
Do you have a death wish?

155
00:10:19,910 --> 00:10:21,510
I'll only say this once.

156
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:23,030
Your name is Chou.

157
00:10:23,270 --> 00:10:25,960
You're the lowest-ranking servant
at Wangshi Tower.

158
00:10:30,150 --> 00:10:32,080
You were injured
after falling off a cliff.

159
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:34,030
It was me who spent money and manpower

160
00:10:34,030 --> 00:10:35,720
to pull you back from death's door.

161
00:10:36,030 --> 00:10:37,480
You don't even know gratitude.

162
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:39,120
Yet you dare disrespect your master.

163
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:40,550
Did you deserve that?

164
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:43,030
How would I know

165
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:45,720
whether you're telling the truth?

166
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:48,120
Don't believe me?

167
00:10:49,870 --> 00:10:51,360
Then leave.

168
00:10:51,630 --> 00:10:54,240
But Wangshi Tower
spent eighteen years raising you.

169
00:10:54,630 --> 00:10:56,270
And your medical expenses

170
00:10:56,270 --> 00:10:57,670
were paid with real silver.

171
00:10:57,870 --> 00:10:58,840
All together,

172
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:01,360
you owe this Tower Master
one thousand taels.

173
00:11:03,630 --> 00:11:06,080
Until you've repaid every tael,

174
00:11:06,390 --> 00:11:07,790
don't even think about leaving.

175
00:11:08,710 --> 00:11:10,680
You've already been idle
for more than ten days.

176
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:12,320
Now that you're awake,

177
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:14,910
clean yourself up and get to work.

178
00:11:25,670 --> 00:11:26,480
That felt great.

179
00:11:26,870 --> 00:11:28,000
So satisfying.

180
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:29,910
Zheng Yuanhe,

181
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:32,750
you made me lose everything
and forced me to run for my life.

182
00:11:33,150 --> 00:11:35,910
Making you my servant
is letting you off easy.

183
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:38,550
Who was it that said

184
00:11:39,150 --> 00:11:40,240
we should bring him back

185
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:41,630
and negotiate with him properly?

186
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:45,080
But who could've seen this coming?

187
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:46,910
He lost his memory.

188
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:51,910
When the one person
who posed the greatest threat to you

189
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:53,870
ended up in your hands,

190
00:11:54,670 --> 00:11:57,080
looking so pale

191
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:59,080
and completely bewildered,

192
00:12:02,080 --> 00:12:06,080
it really brings out your darker side.

193
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:08,840
I'll make him wish he were dead.

194
00:12:26,540 --> 00:12:27,900
(Contract)

195
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:33,000
It's all here in black and white.

196
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:35,510
This contract clearly states

197
00:12:35,720 --> 00:12:37,960
that you can work here

198
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:39,480
to repay what you owe.

199
00:12:40,320 --> 00:12:41,750
Once it's all paid off,

200
00:12:41,870 --> 00:12:43,270
you'll be free.

201
00:12:44,870 --> 00:12:46,030
Put your thumbprint on it.

202
00:12:46,940 --> 00:12:49,180
(Contract)

203
00:12:49,510 --> 00:12:50,390
I

204
00:12:51,790 --> 00:12:52,630
won't sign.

205
00:12:55,150 --> 00:12:56,750
That's not up to you.

206
00:13:15,320 --> 00:13:16,910
I'll ask you one last time.

207
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:18,550
Are you signing or not?

208
00:13:23,150 --> 00:13:24,720
Just wait until I recover.

209
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:27,870
You'll be the first one I kill.

210
00:13:28,630 --> 00:13:31,200
Then I'll make sure
that day never comes.

211
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:32,480
(You jerk.)

212
00:13:32,750 --> 00:13:34,030
(You ruined my rice balls,)

213
00:13:34,360 --> 00:13:35,720
(stole my newspaper office,)

214
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:37,390
(and burned down my bank.)

215
00:13:37,720 --> 00:13:38,750
(I'll beat you to death.)

216
00:13:41,870 --> 00:13:43,200
If you won't sign,

217
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:45,000
then I won't tell you

218
00:13:45,150 --> 00:13:46,480
who you really are.

219
00:13:48,270 --> 00:13:49,320
I...

220
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:53,960
I'll sign.

221
00:14:06,980 --> 00:14:09,660
(Contract)

222
00:14:11,300 --> 00:14:13,420
(Contract Holder: Chou)

223
00:14:16,600 --> 00:14:18,320
Now that you've signed,

224
00:14:18,720 --> 00:14:19,240
from now on,

225
00:14:19,240 --> 00:14:20,550
you'll call me Master.

226
00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:24,080
Call!

227
00:14:32,270 --> 00:14:33,200
Mas...

228
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:36,840
Mas...ter.

229
00:14:42,600 --> 00:14:44,150
Good.

230
00:14:56,820 --> 00:15:00,180
♪Snowflakes settle gently
upon your brows♪

231
00:15:00,940 --> 00:15:04,340
♪Your dark hair
brushes across my fingertips♪

232
00:15:05,100 --> 00:15:06,860
♪Your smile♪

233
00:15:07,100 --> 00:15:09,380
♪Melts away the winter snow♪

234
00:15:09,380 --> 00:15:13,060
♪One fleeting glance says more
than a thousand words♪

235
00:15:13,540 --> 00:15:16,860
♪Yet I stand before you♪

236
00:15:17,580 --> 00:15:21,420
♪Unable to recognize your eyes♪

237
00:15:21,820 --> 00:15:23,740
♪Though fate tries♪

238
00:15:23,740 --> 00:15:26,340
♪To make us pass each other by♪

239
00:15:26,540 --> 00:15:29,980
♪I choose to make our story whole♪

240
00:15:30,220 --> 00:15:31,860
♪Though time slips by♪

241
00:15:31,860 --> 00:15:33,620
♪As day turns into night♪

242
00:15:34,140 --> 00:15:38,180
♪I still remember
our days at Wangshi Tower♪

243
00:15:38,580 --> 00:15:40,980
♪One glance at you lasts a lifetime♪

244
00:15:40,980 --> 00:15:42,740
♪Blessed by fate♪

245
00:15:42,740 --> 00:15:47,900
♪I believe this moment
will last forever♪

246
00:15:47,900 --> 00:15:50,340
♪Your smiling face♪

247
00:15:50,340 --> 00:15:53,180
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

248
00:15:53,180 --> 00:15:56,820
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

249
00:15:57,340 --> 00:16:00,780
♪And wander the world together♪

250
00:16:00,780 --> 00:16:02,140
♪Holding you close♪

251
00:16:02,140 --> 00:16:04,660
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

252
00:16:04,660 --> 00:16:06,980
♪Your tenderness♪

253
00:16:06,980 --> 00:16:09,860
♪Is the brightest moon♪

254
00:16:09,860 --> 00:16:13,540
♪I'd rather
pledge three lifetimes to you♪

255
00:16:14,060 --> 00:16:17,380
♪Our love will never fade away♪

256
00:16:17,380 --> 00:16:19,820
♪Though heaven and earth grow old♪

257
00:16:20,340 --> 00:16:24,620
♪My heart will remain forever pure♪

258
00:16:34,100 --> 00:16:36,260
♪Your smiling face♪

259
00:16:36,420 --> 00:16:39,020
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

260
00:16:39,340 --> 00:16:43,180
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

261
00:16:43,420 --> 00:16:46,900
♪And wander the world together♪

262
00:16:46,900 --> 00:16:48,220
♪Holding you close♪

263
00:16:48,220 --> 00:16:50,860
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

264
00:16:50,860 --> 00:16:53,140
♪Your tenderness♪

265
00:16:53,140 --> 00:16:55,980
♪Is the brightest moon♪

266
00:16:55,980 --> 00:16:59,740
♪I'd rather
pledge three lifetimes to you♪

267
00:17:00,180 --> 00:17:03,540
♪Our love will never fade away♪

268
00:17:03,540 --> 00:17:06,180
♪Though heaven and earth grow old♪

269
00:17:06,460 --> 00:17:10,580
♪My heart will remain forever pure♪
